Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏面盡失  我向井均一生的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我也被拉到這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您屈駕到鄙店真是對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  為了我這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼話  西村先生的店就像我們的家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失去了的話  我們可不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥也說過同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你哥哥是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是阿俊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個很擅長格鬥遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來最近很少見到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們該怎麼辦呢  少校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  人數不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島中將可不能算為戰鬥力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行  棒球根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  算上玫歐也只有六人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  玫歐完全不懂棒球的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成連我也算在內了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣姑且…能打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要取勝的話  有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練由我來擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  在那個夏天最後的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們練起了棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺  時光飛逝

Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}一棒 明老闆   二壘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}二棒 阿宏     中外野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}三棒 阿哲     三壘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}四棒 岩男     左外野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}五棒 第四代   投手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}六棒 西村先生 游擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}七棒 少校     捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}八棒 電杆     右外野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}九棒 玫歐     一壘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}教練  愛麗絲!
